eases range, a pair of drop tanks are carried. Since the Mirage 2000N\'s standard weapon was the ASMP, which was carried on the centerline pylon, that meant it couldn\'t carry a centerline tank, but a distinctive big 2,000 liter (530 US gallon) underwing drop tank with a bulbous nose was developed to more than compensate.','Dassault Mirage 2000N (In-cockpit cameras)','','publish','closed','closed','','auto-draft-26','','','2017-03-22 13:14:30','2017-03-22 13:14:30','',0,'http://54.172.133.99/komandov3/watch/videos_library/auto-draft-26',0,'videos_library','',0),(1647,1,'2017-03-22 04:06:04','2017-03-22 04:06:04','','460737452_640','','inherit','open','closed','','460737452_640','','','2017-03-22 04:06:04','2017-03-22 04:06:04','',1640,'http://54.172.133.99/komandov3/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/460737452_640.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1649,1,'2017-03-22 04:06:34','2017-03-22 04:06:34','Komputer Kindergarten / Madeleine, January 2014\r\n\r\nThis is a character based on radio/tv personality Kim Komando who teaches us how to use computers and how to live life.','First Life workshop - \"does it blow up?\"','','publish','open','open','','auto-draft-22','','','2017-03-22 04:07:56','2017-03-22 04:07:56','',0,'http://54.172.133.99/komandov3/watch/1649/auto-draft-22',4,'post','',0),(1650,1,'2017-03-22 04:07:01','2017-03-22 04:07:01','','458085690_640','','inherit','open','closed','','458085690_640','','','2017-03-22 04:07:01','2017-03-22 04:07:01','',1646,'http://54.172.133.99/komandov3/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/458085690_640.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1652,1,'2017-03-21 04:07:31','2017-03-21 04:07:31','The Dassault Mirage 2000N is a variant of the Mirage 2000 variant (based on the Mirage 2000B two-seat trainer, but features considerable changes) designed for nuclear strike which was intended to carry the Aerospatiale Air-Sol Moyenne Portee (ASMP) nuclear stand-off missile. It forms the core of the French air-based tactical nuclear deterrent. The Mirage 20